{"word":"οὐδαμός","slug":"οὐδαμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n75759\" key=\"ou)damo/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οὐδᾰμ-ός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ή</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδὲ ἀμός</foreign>, <sense id=\"n75759.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">not any one, no one</tr_>, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">like</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">οὐδείς</ref></xr>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg001:57:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pron.\">Pron.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">57.2</biblScope> </bibl>: used only in pl. and only by <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> writers ( <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδένες</foreign>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">, οὐδαμοί, οὐδαμῶν</foreign>, etc., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">none</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.18</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:57\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">57</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πρήγματα . . οὐδαμῶν Ἑλληνικῶν τῶν οὐ πολλὸν μέζω</foreign>, i.e. much greater than any Greek power, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:145\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.145</biblScope> </bibl>: rarely in fem., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδαμὰς ἄλλας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:114\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.114</biblScope></bibl></cit>.—Cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδαμός</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}